{{term|term= adipocytes |content= [[adipocyte]]s }}{{defn|1= A major cell type of insects that stores fat body and reserves nutrients.}}

{{term|term= admarginal |content= admarginal }}{{defn|1= (adjective): Along the margin.}}

{{term|term= aedeagus |content= [[aedeagus]] }}{{defn|1= The sclerotized terminal portion of the male genital tract that is inserted into the female during insemination. Its shape is often important in separating closely related species.}}

{{term|term= aestivation |content= [[aestivation]] }}{{defn|1= Summer dormancy, entered into when conditions are unfavourable for active life i.e. it is too hot or too dry.}}

